  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Les Bergers is the ideal base for the perfect ski holiday in <a data-udi="umb://document/acff50eb9ad84862a464f68b551bc497" href="/{localLink:umb://document/acff50eb9ad84862a464f68b551bc497}" title="Alpe d'Huez">Alpe d'Huez</a>. Enjoy an après-ski drink in one of the sunniest resorts in the Alps on the hotel’s south facing, piste-side terrace or take in the snowy scenery of the slopes, glacier or valley from the hotel's modern bedrooms. </p>
<h2>Unbeatable location</h2>
<p>The hotel sits in a fantastic position on the side of the piste. You'll also have easy access to the huge Grand Domine ski area - totalling around 250km - and the snow park. If you feel like taking a day off of the slopes, there'll also be plenty of opportunities for non-ski activities around the resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/acff50eb9ad84862a464f68b551bc497" href="/{localLink:umb://document/acff50eb9ad84862a464f68b551bc497}" title="Alpe d'Huez">Alpe d'Huez</a>, like husky sledding and snowshoeing.</p>
<h2>Perfect for families </h2>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/acff50eb9ad84862a464f68b551bc497" href="/{localLink:umb://document/acff50eb9ad84862a464f68b551bc497}" title="Alpe d'Huez">Alpe D'Huez</a> has been awarded the Family Plus Label meaning Hotel Les Bergers is a great option for children looking to make new friends on your family ski holiday. There are multiple children's clubs accommodating from 18 months to 17 years of age, providing all the fun from snow ball fights, games and challenges, mini discos and shows.</p>
<h2>Wellness facilities</h2>
<p>The spa is a time for escape and relaxation and we're sure you'll make the most of the facilities Hotel Les Bergers has to offer. The adult only wellness area has a whirlpool, sauna and steam room as well as a new outdoor pool and Nordic bath - the best relief for your muscles at the end of an active day.</p>
<h3>Why is this an Inghams' Choice property?</h3>
<p><strong>Great location</strong> - Hotel Les Bergers is in an ideal location just a short 3 minutes' walk away from the centre of the Bergers area of Alpe d'Huez.</p>
<p><strong>Spa and wellness facilities</strong> - With access to a sauna, steam room and new outdoor pool, Hotel Les Bergers give you the chance to really sit back and relax on your winter holiday. </p>
<p><strong>Piste side location</strong> - Hotel Les Bergers is located on the side of the piste, providing easy access to the huge ski area of Alpe d'Huez, and there's nothing better than being able to put your skis and boots on at the door and go.</p>]]></description>
