  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>Located in the Bergers are of Alpe d'Huez, Hotel Les Bergers is in an ideal position at the foot of the slopes with ski to the door access. </p>
<p>The nearest lift is only 50 metres away from the hotel and there is an in house partner ski hire shop so collecting your equipment and hitting the slopes couldn't be easier.</p>
<p>It is also only a minute's walk to the ski school meeting place.</p>]]></locationDescription>
